highlights.text: Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Kolkata. “Kesariya” is the highest at #3.
“WOH” by Ikka, Dino James, and Badshah is the highest new entry on Top Songs Kolkata at #69.
“Jehda Nasha (From "An Action Hero")” by Tanishk Bagchi, Faridkot, Yohani, Amar Jalal, and Harjot Kaur is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Kolkata, up 47 spots at #33.
“Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Kolkata the longest, at 62 weeks straight.
